name: Blighted Elegance Postbox
text: Amidst a dying garden's grip, the mailbox, with its ornate, sinister twist, stood—a beacon of morbid beauty. Villagers whispered of its curse, a relic dispersing dread. Enthralled by its design, none dared approach, save the old crone who'd caress its carvings, murmuring secrets to unseen specters.
